Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before arriving at their next destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and crew stopped at Spa Island to enjoy a vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and met the sisters, Sayo and Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Sea Raccoon, named Munki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you were, #100.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, it's been a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:04.42,Attack notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Gum Gum Bazooka!{*Gomu Gomu no Bazooka!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That notebook. That was Foxy's target, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook has directions on how to create a gem written inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please save us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy arrived with the intention of stealing the notebook entrusted to the girls by their father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It contains the secret behind creating a gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and crew managed to defeat them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo was taken hostage by the true enemy, Doran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:43.69,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx155\fscy135\pos(638,587)\fad(2000,2000)}Collapse!    The Spa Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:43.69,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx102.5\fscy138.75\pos(646,180)\fad(2000,2000)}Great Treasure Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is filled with traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pathetic, Foxy the Silver Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To escape via a trap of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we have to do is wait for them to discover the secret behind the gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really can't understand much from this alone, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already searched all over this ship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no big X anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? This memo must be fake after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, big sis has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save big sis Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh? You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to see that gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Even though this gem could be a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what do we do, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we destroy this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EH?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Sayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we destroy it, we will find her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the hint about the gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying it would make searching easier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and start this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, just thinking about whether something is or isn't on this island is pointless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all are seriously lacking in delicacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, more than anything else, I can't stand listening to anything that artichoke mustache fool told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really doesn't matter if this ship sinks, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, even Robin is in on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, nobody is going to stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Captain's orders after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you do understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you take care of Sunny Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we rarely come to such a resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:08.05,Attack notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: 108 Pound Cannon{*Hyaku Hachi Poundo Hou!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{*Concasse!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.73,Attack notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Gum Gum Whip!{*Gomu Gomu no Muchi!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.47,Attack notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Tabasco Star!{*Tabasuko Boshi!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.28,Attack notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Carving Hoof Sakura{*Kokutei Roseo!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{*Thunderbolt Tempo!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{*Clutch!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.61,Attack notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Three-Verse Humming: Arrow-Notch Slice{*Hanauta Sanchou Yahazu Giri!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like such bullets would be effective against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He deflected the bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards, you sure did it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Weaponsu Lefto!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry up and return Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT IS THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! A hostage situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can go all out and do as you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think this Spa Island cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shitty bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bis sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to send this little girl flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Initially, I wanted to have you solve the mystery of that notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but, forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only after that, will I return her.{After I get it, I will return her./I'll return her after I get it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you the notebook, so return big sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sis Sayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina, solve the secret of the notebook, and complete father's research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in our father, Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hand over his research to these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that father tried to accomplish his dream, for the sake of us and the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you. Don't lose our father's dream, for my sake.{For my sake, don't abandon father's dream.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie. Father was merely a selfish researcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.97,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:29.25,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think father will enjoy this birthday cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:29.98,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.09,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.63,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have discovered something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:44.97,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.89,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.99,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.32,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:20.08,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,So they made cake for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.28,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.73,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:29.79,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.59,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,30 year old cast-off bug skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.50,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be useful for my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.88,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have gone through metamorphosis 30 years ago tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.66,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.13,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! But, last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:47.16,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ah, ah, ah, ahh, cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.10,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure is a tasty looking cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:49.85,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.51,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, that cake...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.38,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I made it yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:01.53,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,but it may have gone bad. It's summer after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.43,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor. Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.52,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,He already examined you and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't understand anything about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't thinking about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. This isn't the time for you siblings to be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina, you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.44,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad about the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.50,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:42.46,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been looking forward to the birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:43.40,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:49.46,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the 30 year old cast-off, there is an ingredient necessary for gem creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:53.31,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't taken this opportunity, I would have had to wait another 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.87,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't avoid going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.32,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.21,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:58.96,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.58,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.92,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lina must definitely be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:10.82,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just like your mother, but Lina is more like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.70,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,When she gets angry, she doesn't let it go easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:19.51,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,When the gem is made, let us all eat a large cake, this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:20.65,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.33,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,The size should surprise Lina as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nuki is saying that it is all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the reason your father left home was to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you two from villains who were targeting his research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.83,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.01,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't easily find a four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:05.40,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,But, big sis found three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:11.31,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because your sister believed that she will definitely find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:12.81,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Believes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.87,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.69,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Research and four-leaf clover hunts are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:20.57,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe, never give up, and work hard, you will always succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.00,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:27.14,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Then I will find a five-leaf clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.72,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Five-leaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.21,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,That is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.35,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.49,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.02,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it! A five-leaf clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.47,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.01,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:49.03,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! I really believed I would find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.07,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Lina! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.23,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:58.55,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Lina! I will do my best as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is father's dream, so it will definitely come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hand over the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:30.86,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:38.37,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Chat with us at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.83,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.62,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{*Seis Fleur!*}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:46.46,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Successive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.00,Attack notes,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Tabasco Star!{*Tabasuko Boshi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:47.50,Attack notes,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{*Boshi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.00,Attack notes,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{*Boshi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.97,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:54.53,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.59,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.60,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and untie her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.74,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.44,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,A lock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.48,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,From where did you climb up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.45,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.34,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.25,Attack notes,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Three-Bladed Style{*Santouryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.46,Attack notes,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Giant Metal Slash!{*Dai Tetsu Giri!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.30,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,EH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.47,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are doing a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.02,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,No, you do some work too damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:57.71,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.67,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.16,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,He released all of the ship's ballasts at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:08.46,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.95,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.06,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:23.98,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.01,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{*Gear Thirdo!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.55,Attack notes,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}TL Note: Bone Balloon!{*Hone Fuusen!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.98,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,{*Giganto Axe!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.26,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.52,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.94,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Heading out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.76,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! Leave us a damn escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.95,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:44.21,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I forgot that I become tiny when I use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:44.86,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.29,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Think about what will happen after, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.46,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,A large X!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.24,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.97,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.05,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,The X mark, and it is so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:43.94,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That underwater volcano is what father had drawn on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:48.66,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Doran built that ship on top of the treasure he was searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:53.49,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,For him to not have realized that the key to the secret was under his feet makes him the biggest idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.27,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.10,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.68,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,That is a... round rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:16.69,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen a round rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:18.09,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.81,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,A mystery rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:22.99,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.19,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.24,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.39,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:35.09,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, the Round Rainbow is called, "The Gem of the Seas".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.71,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.09,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.09,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way this is the treasure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.77,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.35,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.76,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you guys have the entire treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.81,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.77,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That rainbow is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.00,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,The order of the colors is the opposite of a normal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.27,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,The order of colors?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.19,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.64,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.63,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx112.5\fscy97.5\pos(640,706)\fad(300,300)}-A few days later-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:21.83,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:22.57,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.25,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.50,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,It's the monster raccoon from that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.39,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's sea raccoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.74,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.89,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:39.52,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It looks like Sayo's instincts from that time were right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.81,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother Luffy and everyone else, are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:49.01,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,After we left you, we immediately returned home and tried what Big sis thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:53.83,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,According to my father's formulas, we made 7 varieties of chemical,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:57.86,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,and by mixing them using the same order as a Round Rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.80,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.51,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,They said that they made the gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.64,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:20.09,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo, Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:27.51,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:29.40,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:33.61,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,They all say, "Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:35.54,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get a better look, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:37.62,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,-Huh? Let's see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:40.82,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! It isn't a toy you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:41.67,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:47.42,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:50.12,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It is candy rain! Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.39,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.15,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I dropped the gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:56.01,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:56.60,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:57.35,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.85,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, and search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.84,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,You all, SEARCH FOR IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.38,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.78,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so excited, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:17.12,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,After having gotten to know each of you so well, I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.16,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,I shall work hard to become a 'true' friend to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:21.70,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,True friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:23.80,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't something that happens by putting in hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:24.88,Default,Visit us at http,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.92,Default,Next time on One Piece,0000,0000,0000,,Brook's Hard Struggle
