Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:34.75,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx81.25\fscy123.75\pos(637,591)}The Difficult Path to Becoming a True Crewmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.04,Default,Next time on One Piece,0000,0000,0000,,The Difficult Path to Becoming a True Crewmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:32.29,Default,Next time on One Piece,0000,0000,0000,,I will become Pirate King!
